/-- The raw `2x2` matrix corresponding to the metric for fermions. -/
def metricRaw : Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) ‚ÑÇ := !![0, 1; -1, 0]

/-- Multiplying an element of `SL(2, ‚ÑÇ)` on the left with the metric `ùìî` is equivalent
